sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User
    participant A as Agent Runtime
    participant S as skills/*/SKILL.md
    participant M as memories/repo
    participant F as artifacts/features/<slug>

    U->>A: feature request / debugging request / docs request
    A->>S: load selected skill contract
    S->>M: read repo rules and project knowledge
    M-->>A: constraints, terminology, workflow rules
    A->>F: read current feature state when present
    F-->>A: analysis / spec / plan / tasks / review state
    A->>S: execute workflow steps
    S-->>A: required reads, outputs, and stop conditions
    A->>F: write updated artifacts
    F-->>A: next-step state
    A-->>U: questions, status, or completed result

    Note over A,F: Typical harness path:<br/>init -> session -> memory -> research -> spec-requirements -> visualize -> adr -> plan -> implement -> verify -> handoff
